{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-jsx","path":"/mongolia-2020/2019-08-04-decision","webpackCompilationHash":"869e658fa477bde91ac5","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"motivation"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#motivation","ariaLabel":"motivation permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Motivation"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Jetzt ist es soweit: ich habe bei der Arbeit die Genehmigung für eine 4-monatige Auszeit ("},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sabbatical"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sabbatical"}]},{"type":"text","value":") in 2020 bekommen. Jetzt kann endlich die Organisation der nächsten grossen Reise beginnen !!!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was habe ich denn vor?"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nachdem ich mit meinem neuen Reise-Motorrad (BMW R1200 GS Adventure) Geschmack an längeren Touren gefunden habe (siehe Nordkap Tour 2017), wollte ich nochmals eine "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"noch längere"}]},{"type":"text","value":" Tour machen. Bei der Arbeit gibt es die Möglichkeit Gehalt in Urlaub umzuwandeln. Ich habe fleissig gespart, und kann jetzt für längere Zeit in Urlaub fahren. Von der Projektarbeit passt es auch einigermassen, so dass ich in 2020 für "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4 Monate"}]},{"type":"text","value":" wegfahren möchte."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<-- TODO Link zum Moped hier auf Artikel im Blog -->\n<-- TODO Link zu Nordkapp Tour -->"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ich hatte das letzte Jahr viel über Weltreisen, längere Touren gelesen und Vorträge besucht. In 4 Monaten kann man in der Tat mit dem Motorrad sogar eine Weltreise machen, ein absolut authentischer Vortrag eines Weltreisenden aus meiner Gegend ("},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://weltumrundung-motorrad.de/Meine-Reisen/Weltumrundung/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gerhard Spiegler: Weltumrundung"}]},{"type":"text","value":") hat mir das gezeigt. Die wohl bekannteste Motorrad-Tour um die Welt hatte 106 Tage gedauert: "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Long_Way_Round"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"Long way round\" mit Ewan McGregor und Charley Boorman"}]},{"type":"text","value":", ein Klassiker für Motorradfahrer."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Allerdings muss man in dieser knappen Zeit eher \"um die Welt hetzen\" als die Welt wirklich zu erleben. Und die ganze Organisation um das Motorrad zwischen Kontinenten transportieren zu lassen hat mich auch eher abgeschreckt (mal abgesehen von den Kosten). Warum nicht eine lange Reise ohne Verschiffung machen?"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nach viel Lesen stand der Entschluß fest: "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mein Ziel ist die Mongolei !"}]},{"type":"text","value":" Das Land hat mich schon immer fasziniert, die Weite des Landes, die Gegensätze von Bergen, Hochebenen, Wüsten, die immer noch vorhandene Nomaden-Kultur, und auch etwas die Herausforderung beim Motorradfahren."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Und wie hinkommen? Manche fahren den Weg über Ukraine, Kasachstan. Den habe ich aber durch die kriegsähnlichen Zustände in der Ost-Ukraine durch den Krim-Konflikt ausgeschlossen. Zudem ist der Weg durch Kasachstan \"lang und langweilig\", man muss nur den Film \"Long Way Round\" ansehen."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Durch Reiseberichte stand bald fest: ich möchte den Wegen der alten Seidenstraße folgen. Hier gibt es viele interessante Länder und Menschen, viel alte Kultur, und auch motorradtechnisch mit die schönsten, auch herausfordernsten Strassen der Welt."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"die-geplante-tour"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#die-geplante-tour","ariaLabel":"die geplante tour permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Die geplante Tour"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"europa"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#europa","ariaLabel":"europa permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Europa"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ich möchte am "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"01. Mai 2020"}]},{"type":"text","value":" von zu Hause starten. Ich plane über Osteuropa in die Türkei reisen, am Schwarzen Meer vorbeikommen."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Der Plan ist über diese Länder nach Asien zu fahren:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tschechien"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Slowakei"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ungarn"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Rumänien"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bulgarien"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Türkei"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In Istanbul will ich mindestens einen Tag bleiben, dann aber gleich nach Anatolien weiterreisen."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"der-vordere-orient"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#der-vordere-orient","ariaLabel":"der vordere orient permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Der Vordere Orient"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Über die Türkei möchte ich dann durch den Iran und die sog. STAN Staaten reisen."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Türkei"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Iran"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Turkmenistan"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Usbekistan"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tadschikistan"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kirgistan"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kasachstan"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Es ist offen ob das alles klappt: für Iran, Turkmenistan, Usbekistan, Tadschikistan benötigt man Visa, die gerade für Turkmenistan eher nach Zufall vergeben werden. Zudem weiss man leider nicht, wie sich die Situation im Iran im Jahr 2019/2020 politisch weiterentwickelt. Wenn es Problem gibt wäre ein alternativer Weg um oder über das Kaspische Meer nach Kasachstan."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Im Iran freue ich mich vor allem auf die Menschen. Alle Reisenden durch den Iran waren begeistert  von der Freundlichkeit und Hilfsbereitschaft der Menschen dort."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Durch Tadschikistan geht es über den "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pamir_Highway"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pamir Highway"}]},{"type":"text","value":" nach Kirgistan. Der Pamir Highway ist eine eigene Herausforderung, auch nur über ein Visum zu bereisen. Der höchste Punkt am Pass liegt auf 4.655 Meter bevor man dann in das landschaftlich sehr schöne Kirgistan kommt."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"mongolei"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#mongolei","ariaLabel":"mongolei permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Mongolei"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In die Mongolei plane über den Westen einzureisen, durch das Altai Gebirge in Russland (eines der Highlights aller Reisenden). Im Westen der Mongolei liegt das Altai Hochgebirge mit Gipfeln bis 4.500 m. Über die Zentralmongolei und Uliastei will ich denn durch die Hochebenen bis in die Haupstadt Ulanbataar reisen."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ich plane spätestens zum Nationalfest (das "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naadam"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Naadam Fest"}]},{"type":"text","value":" zwischen 10.-13. Juli) in der Mongolei zu sein."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In der Mongolei gibt es immer noch wenige befestigte Strassen, der Offroad Anteil wird sicher sehr hoch werden."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"überblick"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%C3%BCberblick","ariaLabel":"überblick permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Überblick"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Die geplante Tour siehst du hier:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"rehype-image","properties":{"src":"Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png","rehyped":"{\"base64\":\"data:image/png;base64,\",\"aspectRatio\":1.7635327635327636,\"src\":\"/static/0bf5989bb2bc9789e6344cb06d25d7d1/b5af0/Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png\",\"srcSet\":\"/static/0bf5989bb2bc9789e6344cb06d25d7d1/aa0b8/Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png 264w,\\n/static/0bf5989bb2bc9789e6344cb06d25d7d1/7b21d/Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png 528w,\\n/static/0bf5989bb2bc9789e6344cb06d25d7d1/b17c9/Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png 1056w,\\n/static/0bf5989bb2bc9789e6344cb06d25d7d1/b5af0/Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png 2112w,\\n/static/0bf5989bb2bc9789e6344cb06d25d7d1/ff4cf/Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png 2476w\",\"srcSetType\":\"image/png\",\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 2112px) 100vw, 2112px\",\"originalImg\":\"/static/0bf5989bb2bc9789e6344cb06d25d7d1/ff4cf/Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png\",\"originalName\":\"Mongolia-2020-tour-plan.png\",\"density\":144,\"presentationWidth\":2112,\"presentationHeight\":1198}"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"center","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Geplante Tour"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Oder du kannst sie bei "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.google.com/maps/@49.3583764,54.9110194,3.86z/data=!4m2!6m1!1s1cLZ-BT91JYC1yVhPoitZd71SLS3JRp33"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google Maps"}]},{"type":"text","value":" auch genauer anschauen."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ich habe grob überschlagen dass die 4 Monate ausreichen sollten. Ich lasse mir aber komplett offen wie ich wieder nach Hause komme. Wenn ich genügend Zeit (und noch Lust ?) habe fahre ich über den Baikalsee, Russland und die Baltischen Staaten/Polen nach Hause."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wenn aber die Zeit durch Probleme mit dem Motorrad oder sonstige nicht planbare Ereignisse knapp wird, schicke ich das Motorrad per Fracht zurück (LKW, Bahn, Flieger) und fliege dann von Ulanbataar nach Hause."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Das ganze ist ein Plan. Ich rechne aber stark damit dass sich der Plan unterwegs ändern wird. Das macht aber auch den Reiz einer solch langen Reise aus."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"und-wie-geht-es-weiter"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#und-wie-geht-es-weiter",